column4: wireless on ubutnu wont show up but i have a wireless card in my macbook
how do i set up wireless with ubuntu on my macbook
you have ubuntu installed on your macbook? maybe the wireless card isn't supported
if the right module was running, you should have an entry in iwconfig. i'd try googling this one. you can't be the first person with this problem. try ubuntuforums.org as well
